data.description: Start your coastal country club lifestyle at Osprey Cove in this tabby sided cottage. Located on a cul-de-sac, this Bent Pine constructed home is a perfect way to enjoy all the area has offer. Members to the club enjoy golf on a Mark McCumber designed course, Tiki Hut for beverages and pub food, Jr. Olympic pool, fitness center, clubhouse, pro shop, boat ramp and day dock, tennis and an authentic, friendly community. Close to beaches, international airport and the finest health care that includes Mayo Clinic. The home enjoys a maintenance free tabby exterior, high ceilings, bonus room up, new appliances and a screened lanai onto a private backyard. Play, Relax, Explore, your coastal life starts here!
